Class SourceEnricherListenerManager

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, CvTermEnricherListener<Source>, EnricherListener<Source>, SourceEnricherListener, AliasesChangeListener<CvTerm>, AnnotationsChangeListener<CvTerm>, CvTermChangeListener, IdentifiersChangeListener<CvTerm>, SourceChangeListener, XrefsChangeListener<CvTerm>
    public class SourceEnricherListenerManager
extends CvTermEnricherListenerManager<Source>
implements SourceEnricherListener
    A manager for listeners which holds a list of listeners. Listener manager allows enrichers to send events to multiple listeners. A listener itself, it implements all methods which will then fire the corresponding method in each entry of the listener list. No contract is given to the order in which the listeners are fired.
    Since:
    08/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
